name: Placeable Seed Shed
description: Beautifully detailed shed with a drive through design for easy loading and unloading of seed, chemicals, and fertilizers in pallet or tote form. 3d electric roll up doors at both ends for quick easy access. The roll up doors and man doors are controlled by manual triggers while the lights are on automatic sensors. 3d tin well detailed custom concrete textures. I have tried something new with this file to cut down the file size tremendously, nearly 300mb has been saved. With that being said after 20 plus hours of testing we have not found any issues with this new method. If you have any issues please report them back so they can be addressed. There are different colored version in the store.  Enjoy!
